{"type": "article", "id": 24928, "title": "Saint Laurent 新创意总监确定，以及，KENZO 推出花花的胶囊系列｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-04-05T09:24:20Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 18072, "name": "创意总监"}, {"id": 862, "name": "设计师"}, {"id": 25793, "name": "副牌"}, {"id": 10667, "name": "升职"}, {"id": 5040, "name": "酒杯"}, {"id": 6582, "name": "春夏"}, {"id": 1364, "name": "音乐节"}, {"id": 25794, "name": "Versus Versace"}, {"id": 325, "name": "Fendi"}, {"id": 3340, "name": "Valentino"}, {"id": 2002, "name": "Balmain"}, {"id": 5170, "name": "Moncler"}, {"id": 686, "name": "adidas"}, {"id": 671, "name": "Gucci"}, {"id": 253, "name": "LINE"}, {"id": 24249, "name": "Anthony Vaccarello"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 39, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702133703VzgmCRa8HDqciB4y.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>一些重要的新闻：</h2>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/designer-luxury/saint-laurent-confirms-anthony-vaccarello-hire-10402936/\"><b>Versus Versace 创意总监成为Saint Laurent 新创意总监</b></a>｜ 继  Saint Laurent 创意总监确认离职后，范思哲 (Versace) 旗下副牌 <a href=\"http://www.racked.com/2016/4/4/11360100/anthony-vaccarello-versus-versace\">Versus 创意总监 Anthony Vaccarello 也紧接着卸任</a>。昨晚<a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/designer-luxury/saint-laurent-confirms-anthony-vaccarello-hire-10402936/\"> <i>WWD</i> 又报道</a> Saint Laurent 母公司开云宣布 Vaccarello  即刻起担任 Saint Laurent 创意总监。36 岁的 Vaccarello 兼有比利时和意大利血统，毕业后加入 Fendi，2008 年在巴黎创立了个人同名品牌。2013 年曾任 Versus Versace 特邀创意总监，2015 年初刚刚成为 Versus Versace 正式常任创意总监。10 月的 2017 春夏秀场将会是他在 Susan Chokachi 的首秀。</p>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://fashionista.com/2016/04/valentino-buying-balmain\"><b>Valentino 可能将并购 Balmain</b></a>｜2012 年被卡塔尔皇室收购的 Valentino 近日据报道希望以 5 亿欧元（约合 5.69 亿美元）收购法国品牌 Pierre Balmain，同时参与的还有一家中国集团以及美国投资者。上月就传出 Balmain 创始人的继承人 Alain Hivelin 欲出售品牌，报道称本周四他将决定最后是否由 Valentino 接手。<br></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://sg.fashionmag.com/news/Gucci-Susan-Chokachi-promoted-as-America-s-CEO,676485.html#.VwKW0oQrJQY\"><b>Gucci 美国区行政经理升至当地 CEO</b></a>｜Susan Chokachi 继续在 Gucci 升职，升至 Gucci 美国地区总裁兼 CEO，从 1998 年起加入 Gucci，此后就保持了 Gucci 美国地区业绩不断增长，直到 2009 年她被任命为市场营销及通讯部门高级副总裁，同时掌管品牌美国地区行政管理经理。</p>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/legal/moncler-anti-counterfeit-technology-10402777/\"><b>Moncler 将使用高科技防伪芯片</b></a>｜从春季系列开始，Moncler 的所有产品将会使用一种革命性的防伪系统，利用最近发展的无线电频率识别技术。品牌的 logo 内将会加入独特的字母数字码、二维码和近场通讯标签。<br></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://us.fashionmag.com/news/H-M-to-expand-in-Mexico-enter-Puerto-Rico,677500.html#.VwMCg4QrJQY\"><b>H&amp;M 继续在墨西哥扩张</b></a>｜瑞典快时尚零售巨头 H&amp;M 继 2015 年在墨西哥开了 8 家店后，今年将在墨西哥新开 10 家店，目前共 16 家，预计 2016 年将在当地雇用 700 名新员工。H&amp;M 也持续关注南美地带，将在波多黎各（Puerto Rico）开店，此前进驻的南美地区包括墨西哥、智利和祕鲁。</p>\n<h2>一些值得一看的：</h2>\n<p class=\"\">Giorgio Armani 2016 新的<a href=\"http://wwd.com/media-news/fashion-memopad/giorgio-armani-frames-of-life-2016-ads-10401720/\"> Frames of Life 眼镜系列广告</a>，找来了美食博主、芭蕾舞者、室内设计师和电影导演等不同职业人来拍摄，展现不同的生活方式。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133644WyodVOQmHLtFglEM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.50648148\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133644AITmiD6Ly9XMz2NJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133645yh52fZxnBARzPEVI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133645kShM2wuV4RdnJ9zL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133646KB34ZlAYPkuHM7xh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133646N7tC8Uc6rpy1wboj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133647F2qcICskwjD6OR5A.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">Adidas Tennis 和 Y-3 合作推出了一个<a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/4/adidas-tennis-y-3-2016-collection\">网球系列</a>，斑马纹是亮点：<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133647QWNpTz2a938RyqA5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133648EXUWx2GO56j3V0bA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133648vt1KmSqTHWsV7Y6o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133649HlhMczG89J1Kvs36.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133650eCQDvXcE9GAlmn51.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">Line Friends 粉丝可能会喜欢这个周边——<a href=\"http://popbee.cn/lifestyle/linefriendswine-glasss/\">酒类的套装</a>，包括布朗和可妮表情的高脚杯，以及布朗熊样子的瓶塞：<br></p>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021336507D0ZxXjhzw9BFCSo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133651mW27fou5EeIvRSZ9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133651aoOqvc4XKCjGMrtl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133652BWPxwje6qFzQuSd7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133652i8PhHFaCBkG0IfcQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/free-people-april-2016-catalog-festival-fashion/\">Free People 四月特辑</a>，都是直接穿去音乐节的行头 ：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021336534TNgE8K0zhyZ3AUY.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.81296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021336544Z5kBlmTKdpAFS8o.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.2975\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133654DuRPYeTst4Av8IWr.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133655m6OwpKvIgPzWteGQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.82375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133656lVfhRWEB8IuFk7s9.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67407407\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021336569JrktA7Q1XvlYB2M.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71944444\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"> KENZO 为庆祝迪士尼电影《The Jungle Book》（森林王子）即将上映，推出色彩斑斓的 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/4/kenzo-the-jungle-book-capsule-collection\">The Jungle Book × KENZO 合作胶囊系列</a>：<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133657aDWMtU43IxHor5nQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133657P8qreVY6WOMRZsb2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133658qen29a6vRopFy7zM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021336584Vr6j5XUm0wQCyeu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133659I8dbLushOGzP2Ro0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/4/public-school-2016-ss-campaign\">Public School 在纽约街头拍摄了黑白的春夏广告</a>：<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133700uTRQyztIrpx0WLvm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75498008\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133701n5mILuYwGKx6v2hU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75498008\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133702OY0ncEG9KAV3yohS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75498008\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><br></p>\n\n"}